{"tid":1309860,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王嘉爾IG突然「取關一半名單」傳和Mark有關　粉絲和團飯戰翻：少團魂綑綁！","createTime":"2019-07-12T11:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T12:02:05.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7acaab4615d1118691247b2b1aa9ef394a8548d5","tid":1309860,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:35:00.000Z","msg":"南韓日前掀起「直播主之亂」，意外爆出疑似偶像男團GOT7的Mark與一名女直播主的地下情。雖然女直播主事後表示她跟MARK一點都不熟，對話內容都是謠言，但相隔4天MARK本人也在官咖上留言寫下：「我知道我讓你們失望了。」成員們近來更大動作將IG關注名單清空，只剩下關注彼此，卻也另外再爆出「王嘉爾粉絲」和「GOT7團飯」的爭執。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4230/4230925.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4230%2F4230925.jpg&h=456060e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GOT7團員們IG接連將追蹤名單清空，王嘉爾則刪了一半好友。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\nGOT7團員們近來紛紛將IG關注名單清空，被猜測是與先前Mark意外捲入直播主之間的爭議有關。但7名團員中，最常有國際合作機會的王嘉爾（Jackson）卻是唯一沒有清空名單的人。雖然目前王嘉爾IG仍關注377人，但在這之前，他的關注名單多達600多人，等於清除了快一半。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4230/4230926.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4230%2F4230926.jpg&h=cbef670a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Mark的IG關注名單，只剩下GOT7官方帳號和團員們。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n此事意外引起「王嘉爾粉絲」和「GOT7團飯」的爭執，團飯們認為，團員們一起清空名單，不僅是力挺兄弟的表現，更能避免其他團員以後也發生類似的爭議。但王嘉爾粉絲則持不同看法，認為是公司要求這麼做，不悅地表示：「那些人脈都是王嘉爾累積下來的，憑什麼要以團魂綑綁，要求取消關注他的朋友。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4230/4230927.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4230%2F4230927.jpg&h=07456794&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼王嘉爾取消關注了將近一半好友。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4230/4230928.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4230%2F4230928.jpg&h=de657538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王嘉爾粉絲在意的點，還包括許多國際合作，常常是藝人們三言兩語在IG上促成的，認為此舉會害王嘉爾在那些被取消關注的朋友面前非常尷尬。不過仍有一大部份人認為，「公司要求」一事也只是猜想，社群網站怎麼使用是個人自由，外人無需置喙。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4230/4230924.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4230%2F4230924.jpg&h=89ca6077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王嘉爾IG取消關注了一半好友。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\nJYP咩事阿到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b343cf665deaf6edf770a2c3f73c8d663077c9","tid":1309860,"uid":240447,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"收皮啦導狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9db4b45a11155d48b7d1859124b5074e38fca3","tid":1309860,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5b343cf665deaf6edf770a2c3f73c8d663077c9","tid":1309860,"uid":240447,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"收皮啦導狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:38:59.000Z","msg":"抵死阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd955341b5bfdfffcd2ca05ed76168fdf7f0c50","tid":1309860,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:53:23.000Z","msg":"咪連累我哋嘎嘎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d75d6a716026f77bec5e82fca28977504150daf","tid":130986